These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
House: ranch-style, palace, cottage, victorian
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, rock-climbing, hiking, reading
4 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, bridge, whist
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person playing whist is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the cottage house is on the far left##1
4. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person playing bridge and the palace house##2
6. the person playing monopoly is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| House        | cottage | victorian  | palace | ranch-style  |
| Hobby         | reading    | rock-climbing  | video-games       | hiking     |
| Game   | bridge     | billiard | whist       | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, manager, software-developer, fisherman
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rat, rabbit, pony
City: new-york, colone, hannover, rome
1. the manager is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the freelancer##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to rome is between the owner of the pony and the fisherman##2
5. the owner of the pony is the person traveling to colone##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Job         | manager | freelancer    | fisherman  | software-developer |
| Pet   | pony  | hedgehog  | rat   | rabbit    |
| City         | colone | rome | new-york | hannover      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, dancer, accountant, project-manager
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, watermelon, cabbage, onion
House: futuristic, modern, victorian, cottage
1. the modern house is between the cottage house and the dancer##2
2. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating onion##1
4. the accountant is on the far right##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the far left##1
6. the futuristic house is on the right of the nurse##1
7. the victorian house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Job      | dancer | project-manager         | nurse   | accountant    |
| Food         | watermelon | onion | eggplant | cabbage |
| House   | victorian   | modern        | cottage      | futuristic   |

