.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, azalea, zinnia, poppy
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, fanta
There 4 different types of food: lime, apricot, watermelon, cranberry
1. the person eating watermelon is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lime is between the person eating cranberry and the person who growspoppy##2
3. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person eating lime is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
6. the person eating cranberry is between the person drinking 7up and the person eating apricot##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Flower   | poppy        | azalea   | marigold | zinnia |
| Beverage         | juice | 7up | hot-chocolate    | fanta |
| Food     | watermelon       | lime     | cranberry       | apricot    |

