2. the software-developer is the dutch##1
3. the tower house is on the far right##1
4. the thai is on the left of the german##1
5. the teacher is on the right of the doctor##1
6. the doctor is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
7. the software-developer is between the doctor and the art-deco house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | dutch      | thai       | german   |
| House      | art-deco   | farmhouse  | cape-cod | tower     |
| Job      | photographer     | software-developer | doctor        | teacher |

