.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, musical, thriller, family
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, azure, coral, orange
4 different games are played: chess, go, canasta, mah-jongg
1. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person playing go##1
2. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who likes apricot is between the person who likes orange and the person playing canasta##2
6. the person watching musical movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
7. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre    | thriller | musical  | epic | family      |
| Color   | coral  | orange  | apricot | azure |
| Game   | mah-jongg | chess | go | canasta     |

