.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, cain, prince, bongani
City: san-francisco, colone, boston, berlin
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, boat, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person driving the boat is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person driving the train##1
6. the cain-smoker is between the person traveling to colone and the person traveling to boston##2
7. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Cigar          | prince  | cain    | bongani | swisher  |
| City   | boston | berlin       | colone        | san-francisco    |
| Transport         | jet-ski | train | snowmobile  | boat |

