.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, coffee, soy-milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, ritmeester, oliveros, old-henry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, pop, electronic, reggae
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the fan house##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is between the fan reggae and the person drinking tea##2
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan electronic##1
4. the fan electronic is on the right of the fan house##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage         | soy-milk  | tea | coffee | fanta |
| Cigar   | pall-mall  | old-henry | ritmeester   | oliveros         |
| Music-Genre           | house | electronic  | pop   | reggae      |

