.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, badminton, cricket, ice-hockey
4 different games are played: billiard, whist, mah-jongg, canasta
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, ivory, purple, coral
1. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
2. the person playing whist is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
7. the person playing whist is between the person who likes purple and the person playing billiard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Sport          | ice-hockey  | water-polo    | cricket | badminton       |
| Game         | canasta | whist | billiard  | mah-jongg |
| Color   | purple   | coral      | ivory  | grey     |

