4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, montecristo, dunhill, old-henry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, basketball, skateboarding, tennis
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to nizza and the montecristo-smoker##2
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
7. the person who's sport is tennis is the old-henry-smoker##1
8. the person who's sport is cricket is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| City          | paris      | hannover | boston | nizza |
| Cigar         | old-henry   | montecristo  | pall-mall | dunhill |
| Sport   | tennis | cricket   | basketball | skateboarding |

