The people use 4 different means of transport: train, airplane, van, scooter
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, iris, orchid, marigold
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person who growsorchid is the person traveling to nizza##1
3. the person who growsazalea is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the van##2
4. the person driving the van is between the person who growsazalea and the person traveling to paris##2
5. the person driving the van is the person who growsmarigold##1
6. the person driving the train is the person who growsiris##1
7. the person driving the scooter is the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| City    | paris  | marseilles | rome | nizza     |
| Transport   | train | van   | scooter  | airplane    |
| Flower     | iris        | marigold       | azalea      | orchid |

