The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, journalist, writer, entrepreneur
There 4 different types of food: cherry, corn, broccoli, orange
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the entrepreneur is the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching action movies and the journalist##2
4. the writer is on the far left##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating corn##1
6. the person eating cherry is on the far right##1
7. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | action     | drama | superhero       |
| Job      | writer  | entrepreneur | bartender  | journalist |
| Food        | orange  | corn      | broccoli        | cherry      |

