.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-13::.
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, monopoly, poker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, balloon-flower, poppy
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, june, february
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person playing monopoly and the person who growsamaryllis##2
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing whist is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
6. the person playing poker is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Game   | whist | poker  | monopoly       | mah-jongg   |
| Flower      | amaryllis     | balloon-flower | daisy | poppy |
| Birthday        | june        | february | november     | december |

