.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, october, april, january
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, lime, peas
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, blend, havana, siglo
1. the person eating cauliflower is the siglo-smoker##1
2. the havana-smoker is the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person eating peas is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the blend-smoker is between the person eating lime and the person who's birthday is in april##2
6. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
7. the blend-smoker is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday           | october | january | april    | august   |
| Food   | lime      | cucumber   | peas | cauliflower |
| Cigar     | dunhill     | blend       | havana        | siglo    |

