.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, bridge, billiard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, indie, techno, blues
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, ivory, apricot, brown
1. the person playing bridge is the person who likes apricot##1
2. the person who likes brown is the person playing billiard##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is the fan blues##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes ivory is between the fan r&b and the person playing mah-jongg##2
6. the fan techno is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
7. the person who likes emerald is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes ivory##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Game   | bridge   | poker           | mah-jongg         | billiard      |
| Music-Genre     | r&b | techno | blues | indie |
| Color   | apricot     | ivory         | emerald       | brown        |

