The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, poppy, sunflower
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, motorbike, subway, trike
1. the person who growsbellflower is the security-guard##1
2. the project-manager is between the chef and the person driving the motorbike##2
3. the chef is the person who growsiris##1
4. the chef is between the person who growspoppy and the person driving the trike##2
5. the security-guard is on the left of the chef##1
6. the person driving the van is between the person driving the subway and the person who growssunflower##2
7. the person who growsbellflower is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Job      | security-guard | chef | project-manager   | accountant |
| Flower   | bellflower  | iris    | poppy   | sunflower     |
| Transport   | trike  | subway | van | motorbike   |

