3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is between the person eating lime and the person eating tomato##2
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
6. the person driving the van is between the person who likes chestnut and the person driving the scooter##2
7. the person eating lettuce is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
