.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, havana, baccarat, fonseca
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, may, november, march
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, skiing, soccer, badminton
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the baccarat-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is between the fonseca-smoker and the person who's sport is soccer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Cigar        | fonseca | havana | vegafina | baccarat |
| Birthday         | january       | may     | november   | march   |
| Sport   | biathlon | skiing | soccer | badminton |

 